OL,3,CPub-goer killed 66-year-old man in
OL,4,Crage-filled punch, murder trial hears
OL,6,FA 66-year-old died from injuries
OL,7,Foutside of a pub after trying to help
OL,8,Fthe man who punched him in
OL,9,FLeicestershire, a trial has heard.
OL,11,FDavid Darke died in hospital after
OL,12,Fsustaining a head injury outside the
OL,13,FCrown Inn in Appleby Magna on 21
OL,14,FDecember last year.
OL,16,FNathan Gothard, 36, of Church Street
OL,17,Fis accused of killing Darke who died
OL,18,Fin hospital six days after allegedly
OL,19,Fbeing attacked.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
