PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777460573
OL,3,CPub-goer killed 66-year-old man in
OL,4,Crage-filled punch, murder trial hears
OL,6,FGothard sat in the dock on Tuesday
OL,7,Fwearing black glasses and shaking his
OL,8,Fhead at times.
OL,10,FHe denies murder and an alternative
OL,11,Fcount of manslaughter.
OL,13,FAn inquest into his death in February
OL,14,Ffound that Darke's cause of death were
OL,15,Fserious head injuries after being
OL,16,Fpunched and falling backwards onto the
OL,17,Ffloor.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
