CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777460573
OL,3,CPub-goer killed 66-year-old man in
OL,4,Crage-filled punch, murder trial hears
OL,6,FProsecutor, Peter Joyce KC, told the
OL,7,Fjury of seven men and five women that
OL,8,Fthe atmosphere in the Crown Inn on the
OL,9,Fevening of December 21 last year was
OL,10,F"menacing, threatening, argumentative
OL,11,Fand disputing" because of Gothard's
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,FMr Joyce KC said that Darke was hit so
OL,15,Fhard that it killed him and that it
OL,16,Fwas not an act of self-defence by
OL,17,FGothard.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
